                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have several spell sets memmed with each one labled by level
<br />

<br />
So my Dazzle line up has 
<br />

<br />
Group 53
<br />

<br />
but my regular group is
<br />

<br />
Group High 
<br />

<br />

<br />
and then I  have alts memmed like 
<br />

<br />
Group High Buff 1
<br />
Group High Buff 2
<br />

<br />
Which switches out my bottom two slots for alternating buffs.
<br />

<br />
Makes spell switching quick and easy
<br />

<br />

<br />
As to the person who did not know what their spells do, this is a common problem. People reach their new level, but in their new spells and since the new one is Higher, BAM use it. Not realizing that a lower level spell may work better and the new one is only situational.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=750403" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: red"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: normal">Arcady</span></span></span></a>
